      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once golden, add the<strong> chopped pepper </strong>to the pan with the meat-free chick'n</p><p>Add your<strong> ginger paste</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until the pepper is beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
