    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your<strong> soy sauce </strong>with your <strong>toasted sesame oil </strong>and <strong>honey </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
